<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Gruntal drops Informix.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Gruntal drops Informix.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-08-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Gruntal Investment Research said analyst David Takata dropped coverage of Informix Corp.</p>
<p>-- Informix late Thursday reported a second-quarter loss and said it will restate its 1996 results.</p>
<p>-- Takata said in a report &quot;Informix clearly has a number of issues overhanging, which makes the shares inappropriate for many accounts, even those who have patiently held through this troubling period.&quot;</p>
<p>-- stock was off 14/16 to 9-7/8.</p>
</text>
